Output demos/01-complete-workflow.gif

Set Shell bash
Set FontSize 20
Set Width 1800
Set Height 1000
Set Theme "Catppuccin Mocha"
Set Padding 40
Set TypingSpeed 150ms
Set PlaybackSpeed 0.75

Hide
Type "source demos/.demo_venv/bin/activate"
Enter
Type "cd demo_run"
Enter
Type "export PS1='$ '"
Enter
Type "clear"
Enter
Show

Type "python complete_workflow.py"
Sleep 800ms
Enter
Sleep 32s

Sleep 4s
